U.K.’s Decision on News Corp., BSkyB, May Be Challenged by Group, FT Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-06-30T01:06:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-30/group-may-challenge-u-k-decision-on-news-corp-bskyb-ft-says.html
News Corp. (NWSA) ’s bid to buy the 61
percent of  British Sky Broadcasting Group Plc (BSY)  it doesn’t already
own may face a legal challenge from pressure group Avaaz, which
has informed the U.K. Culture Secretary Jeremy Hunt that it will
apply for a judicial review of his decision should he approve
the proposed takeover, the Financial Times reported, without
attribution.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 